---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ask"
  description="Ask the Joscha guide — converse with Joscha Bach's ideas through an AI companion grounded in his corpus."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Ask</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-medium text-ink mb-4">Ask the Guide</h1>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6 font-serif italic text-lg">
        The SOMA guide widget is available on every page — click the guide button in the corner.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The guide is an AI companion trained on Joscha Bach's public corpus — X threads, talks, and podcasts. It thinks in his vocabulary and can walk you through his ideas. It is <em>not</em> Joscha himself.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Sign in with your email to build a persistent relationship with the guide across visits. Voice conversation will be available once a Campus ConvAI agent is wired up.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>